strings:
<voice_0x01000A26><se_high>Bangerz: We made it!
Jessica's in there.
<voice_0x01000A27><se_high>Bangerz: Now let's get this door open. It's a special door, y'know. Only the people of Alexandria know how to open it.
<voice_0x01000A28><se_high>Bangerz: Go on, give it a try if you don't believe me.

<se_def>No matter how you push or pull,
the door doesn't budge. It seems to be locked.

<voice_0x01000A29><se_high>Bangerz: See? I told you!
Only Alexandrians know how to open this door.

<voice_0x01000A30><se_high>Bangerz: Looks like you trust me.
Sorry for doubting you.
<voice_0x01000A2A><se_high>Bangerz: This is an emergency, so I'll show you how to open the door. But you have to promise never to tell anyone!

<voice_0x01000A2D><se_high>Bangerz: Pretty cool, eh?
It opens from the bottom!

<voice_0x01000A2F><se_high>Bangerz: Well, this is as far as I'm goin'.
I'll head back to the village now.
You help Jessica!
